{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"7432","heading":"Clean heavy-duty vehicles","label":"7432 Clean heavy-duty vehicles","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/ch85/schI/ptA","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Appropriations","label":"a Appropriations","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In addition to amounts otherwise available, there is appropriated to the Administrator for fiscal year 2022, out of any money in the Treasury not otherwise appropriated, $600,000,000, to remain available until , to carry out this section.September 30, 2031","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Nonattainment areas","label":"2 Nonattainment areas","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In addition to amounts otherwise available, there is appropriated to the Administrator for fiscal year 2022, out of any money in the Treasury not otherwise appropriated, $400,000,000, to remain available until , to make awards under this section to eligible recipients and to eligible contractors that propose to replace eligible vehicles to serve 1 or more communities located in an air quality area designated pursuant to as nonattainment for any air pollutant.September 30, 2031section 7407 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Reservation","label":"3 Reservation","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Of the funds appropriated by paragraph (1), the Administrator shall reserve 3 percent for administrative costs necessary to carry out this section.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Program","label":"b Program","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the incremental costs of replacing an eligible vehicle that is not a zero-emission vehicle with a zero-emission vehicle, as determined by the Administrator based on the market value of the vehicles;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"purchasing, installing, operating, and maintaining infrastructure needed to charge, fuel, or maintain zero-emission vehicles;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"workforce development and training to support the maintenance, charging, fueling, and operation of zero-emission vehicles; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/b/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fb%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"planning and technical activities to support the adoption and deployment of zero-emission vehicles.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Applications","label":"c Applications","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"To seek an award under this section, an eligible recipient or eligible contractor shall submit to the Administrator an application at such time, in such manner, and containing such information as the Administrator shall prescribe.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Definitions","label":"d Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Eligible contractor","label":"1 Eligible contractor","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to sell, lease, license, or contract for service zero-emission vehicles, or charging or other equipment needed to charge, fuel, or maintain zero-emission vehicles, to individuals or entities that own, lease, license, or contract for service an eligible vehicle; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to arrange financing for such a sale, lease, license, or contract for service.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Eligible recipient","label":"2 Eligible recipient","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a State;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a municipality;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"an Indian tribe; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"D","heading":null,"label":"D","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/2/D","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F2%2FD","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a nonprofit school transportation association.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Eligible vehicle","label":"3 Eligible vehicle","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “eligible vehicle” means a Class 6 or Class 7 heavy-duty vehicle as defined in section 1037.801 of title 40, Code of Federal Regulations (as in effect on ).August 16, 2022","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Greenhouse gas","label":"4 Greenhouse gas","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “greenhouse gas” means the air pollutants carbon dioxide, hydrofluorocarbons, methane, nitrous oxide, perfluorocarbons, and sulfur hexafluoride.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":"Zero-emission vehicle","label":"5 Zero-emission vehicle","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/5/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/5","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F5%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any air pollutant that is listed pursuant to (or any precursor to such an air pollutant); andsection 7408(a) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/5/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7432/d/5","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs7432%2Fd%2F5%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any greenhouse gas.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
